{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/css-gradient-angles","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>效果展示</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/css-gradient-corner.PNG\" alt=\"corner-shape\"></p>\n<h3>代码</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">  <span class=\"token selector\">.corner</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #58a<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>45deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent 15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #58a 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> bottom left<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>135deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent 15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #58a 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> top left<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-45deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent 15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #58a 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> bottom right<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-135deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent 15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #58a 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> top right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50% 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>角度问题</h3>\n<p><strong>平常我们理解的角度应该是下面这样的：</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/normal-angles.png\" alt=\"normal-angles\"></p>\n<p>X轴的正轴是0°，顺时针旋转为负角，逆时针旋转为正角。</p>\n<p><strong>CSS 中的角度：</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/css-angles.png\" alt=\"css-angles\"></p>\n<p>Y轴的正轴是0°，顺时针旋转为正角，逆时针旋转为负角，箭头所指的方向即使渐变的方向，在 CSS 中默认的渐变角度是自上而下的。</p>\n<p>如果按照平常我们理解角的思维来做这个切角的效果的话，肯定免不了折腾，甚至做不出来这个效果。其实对比一下两幅图也就明白了 CSS 渐变角度，那么这个效果就可以自然而然地做出来了。</p>\n<h3>浏览器兼容</h3>\n<p>兼容主流浏览器：Edge + Chrome + Firefox + IE10+</p>\n<h3>代码的可维护性</h3>\n<p>在作者看来上面实现的代码是不够 <strong>DRY</strong> 的，因此要使代码更加容易维护和重用，那对于原生 CSS 来说就有点强人所难了，所以预处理器登场了，例如 SCSS ，可以将上面的代码写成 Mixin ，以便维护和重用，如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\">  <span class=\"token keyword\">@mixin</span> <span class=\"token function\">corner-shape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$bg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$tr</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$bg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>45deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent <span class=\"token variable\">$tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$bg</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> bottom left<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>135deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent <span class=\"token variable\">$tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$bg</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> top left<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-45deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent <span class=\"token variable\">$tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$bg</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> bottom right<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-135deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> transparent <span class=\"token variable\">$tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$bg</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> top right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50% 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.corner </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">@include</span> <span class=\"token function\">corner-shape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>#58a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 15px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>经过编译之后就可以生成和文章开头一模一样的代码了。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/css-gradient-angles/#%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA\">效果展示</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-gradient-angles/#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\">代码</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-gradient-angles/#%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\">角度问题</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-gradient-angles/#%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9\">浏览器兼容</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-gradient-angles/#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E6%80%A7\">代码的可维护性</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/css-gradient-angles","date":"Jul 28, 2016","title":"CSS 渐变的角度问题","tldr":"今天在看《CSS揭秘》这本书的时候，作者用渐变做出了一个切角的效果（把矩形的四个角切掉），她使用 background 属性来制作了这个效果，不得不惊叹作者对于 CSS 的高超运用。但是在我动手做的过程中发现，在 CSS 中渐变的角度似乎和我们平常理解的角度有些许差别，为此查阅了一些资料，果然有出入，所以在此分享一下！","tags":["CSS"]},"timeToRead":2}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 中有趣的 filter 属性","path":"/css-filter-property"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"IE8 兼容性总结","path":"/ie8-compatibility"}},"relatedPosts":[{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 渐变的角度问题","path":"/css-gradient-angles"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"『译』在你的 WordPress 项目中使用 Let's Encrypt SSL","path":"/use-lets-encrypt-in-wordpress"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/ie8-compatibility","tags":["CSS"],"title":"IE8 兼容性总结"}}},{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Gulp and Browser-sync","path":"/use-browser-sync-with-gulp"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 渐变的角度问题","path":"/css-gradient-angles"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/css-filter-property","tags":["CSS"],"title":"CSS 中有趣的 filter 属性"}}},{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"一些我自己常用的优质Apps","path":"/my-favorite-apps"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"利用 TravisCI 自动部署 Hexo blog","path":"/automatic-deploy-hexo-blog-with-travis-ci"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/restyle-with-stylish","tags":["CSS"],"title":"Stylish —— 优雅地刷网页"}}}]}}}